   "source": [
    "# ALICE RL — Standalone Colab (No External Links Needed)\n",
    "\n",
    "**Self-contained** — runs the full ALICE environment *inside* this notebook.\n",
    "No HF Space, no server, no external URLs required.\n",
    "\n",
    "## What this notebook does\n",
    "1. Installs all dependencies\n",
    "2. Embeds the full ALICE environment (task generator, verifier, reward function, curriculum, failure bank, leaderboard)\n",
    "3. Loads a model with 4-bit QLoRA\n",
    "4. Runs GRPO training against the embedded environment\n",
    "5. Shows full analysis: reward curves, curriculum heatmap, failure bank, leaderboard\n",
    "\n",
    "**Runtime:** T4 GPU recommended — Runtime → Change runtime type → T4 GPU\n",
    "\n",
    "**Models (change `MODEL_ID` in cell 2):**\n",
    "- `Qwen/Qwen2.5-0.5B-Instruct` — fastest, ~1 GB\n",
    "- `Qwen/Qwen2.5-1.5B-Instruct` — default, ~3 GB\n",
    "- `Qwen/Qwen2.5-3B-Instruct` — best quality, ~6 GB\n",
    "- `HuggingFaceTB/SmolLM2-1.7B-Instruct` — ~3.5 GB\n",
    "- `google/gemma-3-1b-it` — requires HF token + license acceptance"
   ]
